00:20:25,250 --> 00:20:26,375
TO FIGURE OUT HOW 
EVERYBODY'S RANKED

448
00:20:26,458 --> 00:20:27,791
WITHIN THE GUILD.

449
00:20:27,875 --> 00:20:29,625
GOTTA START WORKING
MY WAY TO THE TOP. 

450
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,833
- WELCOME HOME.
- 'SUP?

451
00:20:32,916 --> 00:20:34,583
- AAH!

452
00:20:34,666 --> 00:20:37,041
YOU GUYS STINK!

453
00:20:37,125 --> 00:20:39,416
WHY DON'T YOU JERKS
WORK OUT AT YOUR OWN HOUSE?

454
00:20:39,500 --> 00:20:41,916
- NOW LUCY, IF WE WANT TO 
WORK TOGETHER LIKE A TEAM,

455
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:43,416
WE GOTTA TRAIN LIKE ONE.

456
00:20:43,500 --> 00:20:45,250
- WE THOUGHT YOU'D LIKE
THE PINK DUMBBELL.

457
00:20:45,333 --> 00:20:46,791
- I DON'T CARE
WHAT COLOR IT IS,

458
00:20:46,875 --> 00:20:48,166
I'M NOT LIFTING
WEIGHTS WITH YOU!

459
00:20:48,250 --> 00:20:49,875
- WE GOTTA KICK IT UP A NOTCH

460
00:20:49,958 --> 00:20:51,875
IF WE WANNA BEAT
LAXUS AND ERZA. 

461
00:20:51,958 --> 00:20:53,291
- AYE, SIR.

462
00:20:53,375 --> 00:20:54,791
- I JUST WANT
A LITTLE PIECE AND QUIET.

463
00:20:54,875 --> 00:20:56,291
NOW GET OUT!
- ( whispers ) DON'T WORRY.

464
00:20:56,375 --> 00:20:57,875
WE'LL TRAIN QUIETLY, LUCY.

465
00:20:57,958 --> 00:20:59,916
- WHY DOES THIS KIND OF
STUFF ALWAYS HAPPEN TO ME?

466
00:21:01,250 --> 00:21:03,291
- I'VE MADE A DECISION.
- HMM?

467
00:21:03,375 --> 00:21:05,208
- OUR TEAM IS READY
FOR THE BIG TIME.

468
00:21:05,291 --> 00:21:07,416
S-CLASS.
- YEAH!

469
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:10,041
CHECK IT OUT!
- HOW DID YOU GET THAT?!

470
00:21:10,125 --> 00:21:12,416
I THOUGHT WE WEREN'T ALLOWED
TO GO ON THE SECOND FLOOR.

471
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:14,125
- WELL, I JUST
CLIMBED THE STAIRS

472
00:21:14,208 --> 00:21:16,458
AND TOOK IT.
- YOU LITTLE CAT BURGLAR!

473
00:21:16,541 --> 00:21:17,875
- ( giggles )
- SINCE THIS IS OUR FIRST

474
00:21:17,958 --> 00:21:19,791
S-CLASS QUEST,
WE DECIDED TO GO WITH

475
00:21:19,875 --> 00:21:21,791
THE SMALLEST REWARD
WE FOUND ON THE BOARD.

476
00:21:21,875 --> 00:21:23,791
BUT SEVEN MILLION
IS STILL A LOT OF JEWEL.

477
00:21:23,875 --> 00:21:25,208
- WE'RE NOT READY FOR IT.

478
00:21:25,291 --> 00:21:26,708
IF THE MASTER KNEW
WE HAD THIS JOB REQUEST,

479
00:21:26,791 --> 00:21:28,500
HE'D BE FURIOUS.

480
00:21:28,583 --> 00:21:29,916
- YEAH, BUT I THINK HE'LL
END UP BEING PROUD OF US 

481
00:21:30,000 --> 00:21:31,666
IF WE ACTUALLY PULL IT OFF.

482
00:21:31,750 --> 00:21:33,666
- ( sighs )
YOU KNOW, THIS MAY BE

483
00:21:33,750 --> 00:21:35,666
THE DUMBEST THING
YOU'VE EVER DONE, NATSU.

484
00:21:35,750 --> 00:21:37,166
IF YOU WANT TO
RISE UP THE RANKS,

485
00:21:37,250 --> 00:21:39,416
YOU SHOULD TRY FOLLOWING
THE GUILD'S RULES.

486
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:40,833
- JEEZ, WE'RE NEVER
GONNA MAKE S-CLASS

487
00:21:40,916 --> 00:21:42,208
WITH THAT KIND OF ATTITUDE.

488
00:21:42,291 --> 00:21:43,750
- YOU CAN HANDLE THIS
ON YOUR OWN.

489
00:21:43,833 --> 00:21:45,125
I'M STAYING RIGHT HERE.

490
00:21:45,208 --> 00:21:47,833
- BUT THE JOB IS SAVING
A TROPICAL ISLAND.

491
00:21:47,916 --> 00:21:49,833
- REALLY?
- MM-HMM.

492
00:21:49,916 --> 00:21:52,041
- ( steel drums playing )

493
00:21:52,125 --> 00:21:54,666
- Both: IT'S THE CURSED
ISLAND OF GALUNA.

494
00:21:54,750 --> 00:21:56,875
- NO WAY.
DEFINITELY NOT GOING NOW.

495
00:21:56,958 --> 00:21:59,416
- I'LL GIVE YOU HALF
THE FISH I CATCH, LUCY.

496
00:21:59,500 --> 00:22:01,083
- WHAT KINDA INCENTIVE 
IS THAT SUPPOSED TO BE?

497
00:22:01,166 --> 00:22:03,250
( scoffs )
- FINE.  WE'RE OUT OF HERE.

498
00:22:03,333 --> 00:22:06,250
- AYE. - THAT'S THE BEST IDEA
YOU'VE HAD ALL DAY.

499
00:22:06,333 --> 00:22:08,958
HOLD ON.  FOR CRYING OUT LOUD,
WOULD YOU USE THE DOOR?

500
00:22:09,041 --> 00:22:10,708
( sighs, gasps )

501
00:22:10,791 --> 00:22:12,625
OH, NO!  THEY LEFT
THE JOB REQUEST HERE.

502
00:22:12,708 --> 00:22:15,125
NOW EVERYBODY'S GONNA THINK
I'M THE ONE WHO STOLE IT.

503
00:22:15,208 --> 00:22:16,291
WHAT DO I DO?

504
00:22:18,875 --> 00:22:20,291
IS THIS FOR REAL?

505
00:22:20,375 --> 00:22:21,541
ON TOP OF THE GIANT REWARD,

506
00:22:21,625 --> 00:22:22,791
YOU ALSO GET A GATE KEY?!

507
00:22:22,875 --> 00:22:26,291
HMM.
( giggles )

508
00:22:26,375 --> 00:22:28,291
HEY, WAIT UP, YOU GUYS!

509
00:22:28,375 --> 00:22:31,083
I'VE DECIDED TO COME ALONG!

510
00:22:31,166 --> 00:22:34,083
- Mirajane: MASTER!

511
00:22:34,166 --> 00:22:35,708
I DON'T KNOW WHAT'S HAPPENED,

512
00:22:35,791 --> 00:22:37,666
BUT ONE OF THE S-CLASS
QUESTS IS MISSING.

513
00:22:40,208 --> 00:22:41,916
- ( spits )

514
00:22:43,166 --> 00:22:45,916
- ( singing in Japanese )

515
00:24:13,291 --> 00:24:15,666
- Happy: WHICH ONE DO YOU THINK
WE SHOULD TAKE, NATSU?

516
00:24:15,750 --> 00:24:18,583
- I DON'T KNOW. SINCE THIS
IS OUR FIRST S-CLASS QUEST,

517
00:24:18,666 --> 00:24:20,416
WE SHOULD PROBABLY
PICK THE EASIEST ONE.

518
00:24:20,500 --> 00:24:23,250
- AYE.  THIS GALUNA ISLAND
JOB LOOKS COOL.

519
00:24:23,333 --> 00:24:26,250
AND LUCY WON'T BE ABLE TO
TURN DOWN THE BONUS REWARD.

520
00:24:26,333 --> 00:24:28,083
- OH, THEN GALUNA ISLAND IT IS.

521
00:24:28,166 --> 00:24:29,458
QUICK, GRAB IT BEFORE
SOMEONE SEES US.

522
00:24:29,541 --> 00:24:30,541
- AYE!

523
00:24:30,625 --> 00:24:33,708
- ( Natsu and Happy speaking )

524
00:24:33,791 --> 00:24:36,000
- Natsu: ALL RIGHT. NOW LET'S
HEAD OVER TO LUCY'S HOUSE

525
00:24:36,083 --> 00:24:38,000
AND GET SOME TRAINING IN
BEFORE IT'S TIME TO LEAVE.

526
00:24:38,083 --> 00:24:39,500
- Happy:
SOUNDS LIKE A PLAN.

527
00:24:39,583 --> 00:24:41,458
HER PLACE COULD USE
A LITTLE TESTOSTERONE.

